---
title: Smokey Chicken & Garlic Crouton Salad with Caramelised Onion & Avocado
description: Tender, smokey chicken pairs perfectly with crunchy garlic croutons in this hearty salad, brought to life with sweet
caramelised onions. Finished with a creamy mayo drizzle, every bite offers a satisfying balance of smokey, sweet and savoury flavours.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
